quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  2,154,"And say not of those slain in God's way, 'They are dead'; rather they are living, but you are not aware"
  2,155,"Surely We will try you with something of fear and hunger, and diminution of goods and lives and fruits; yet give thou good tidings unto the patient"
  2,156,"who, when they are visited by an affliction, say, 'Surely we belong to God, and to Him we return"
  2,157,"upon those rest blessings and mercy from their Lord, and those -- they are the truly guided"
  2,158,"Safa and Marwa are among the waymarks of God; so whosoever makes the Pilgrimage to the House, or the Visitation, it is no fault in him to circumambulate them; and whoso volunteers good, God is All-grateful, All-knowing"
  2,159,"Those who conceal the clear signs and the guidance that We have sent down, after We have shown them clearly in the Book -- they shall be cursed by God and the cursers"
  2,160,"save such as repent and make amends, and show clearly -- towards them I shall turn; I turn, All-compassionate"
  2,161,"But those who disbelieve, and die disbelieving -- upon them shall rest the curse of God and the angels, and of men altogether"
  2,162,therein dwelling forever; the chastisement shall not be lightened for them; no respite shall be given them
  2,163,"Your God is One God; there is no god but He, the All-merciful, the All-compassionate"